Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5), cdbs, qt4-qmake, libqt4-dev, libqzion-dev, libeet-dev
Standards-Version: 3.8.0
Section: libs
Homepage: http://dev.openbossa.org/trac/qedje

Package: libqedje-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libqedje0 (= ${binary:Version}), libqzion-dev, libeet-dev
Description: UI interface library which separates design from logic
 QEdje extends the Qt toolkit with the flexibility of the Edje
 declarative language.
 .
 Edje is a declarative language that simplifies the development of
 complex interfaces separating the UI design from the application
 logic, by providing animations, layouts and simple scripts in a very
 small memory footprint.
 .
 This package contains the development header files.

